/**
 * DemoPropertyCopywriterPage — "AI Listing Copywriter" demo.
 *
 * Two panels, front-end-only mock (no backend, no real LLM):
 *  - LEFT  : a property card. The user switches among sample properties (chips) and a
 *            tone toggle (Professional / Warm).
 *  - RIGHT : the output area. Click "Generate" → a brief "Writing…" state, then 4 channel
 *            blocks are revealed in sequence, each typed out character-by-character:
 *            formal listing, RED (小红书) post, WeChat-moments blurb, selling-points list.
 *            Switching tone re-generates in a visibly different voice.
 *
 * Lets an AI-naive real-estate agent *see* "AI writes all my marketing in seconds".
 * See marketing/strategy/conversion-strategy.md (gitignored).
 */
